column4: Saudi's Prince Alwaleed bin Talal says Tesla valuation "too exuberant" - CNBC
column5: DUBAI  Oct 23 Saudi Arabian billionaire Prince Alwaleed bin Talal said on Monday the valuation of electric car maker Tesla Inc was "too exuberant" for him to invest in the company.

column4: UPDATE 1-Bitcoin is 'Enron in the making'  Saudi Prince Alwaleed says
column5: RIYADH  Oct 23 Billionaire Saudi Prince Alwaleed bin Talal  who owns investment firm Kingdom Holding  expressed skepticism about cryptocurrencies in an interview with CNBC on Monday  warning that bitcoin was like "Enron in the making".
